pan data-text=\"rei\" data-n=\"360\" data-lemma=\"\">r(ei)</span> · <span data-text=\"publicae\" data-n=\"370\" data-lemma=\"\">p(ublicae)</span> · </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Tuuli Ahlholm; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/FZWWPUD6\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/FZWWPUD6</a></div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"la\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Imperatori · Caesari · divi · Antoni\n                    ni · filio · divi · Hadriani · ne\n                    poti · divi · Traiani · Parthi\n                    ci · pronepoti · divi Nervae\n                    abnepoti · Lucio · Aurelio ·\n                    Vero Augusto\"><span data-text=\"Imperatori\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"\">IMP</span>·<span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Caesari\"><span data-text=\"Caesari\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"\">CAESARI</span></span>·<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"divi · Antoni\n                    ni\"><span data-text=\"divi\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"\">DIVI</span>·<span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Antoni\n                    ni\"><span data-text=\"Antoni\n                    ni\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"\">ANTO<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">N͡I</span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>NI</span></span></span>·<span data-text=\"filio\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"\">F</span>·<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"divi · Hadriani\"><span data-text=\"divi\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"\">DIVI</span>·<span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Hadriani\"><span data-text=\"Hadriani\" data-n=\"65\" data-lemma=\"\">HADRIANI</span></span></span>·<span data-text=\"ne\n                    poti\" data-n=\"75\" data-lemma=\"\">NE<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>POTI</span>·<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"divi · Traiani · Parthi\n                    ci\"><span data-text=\"divi\" data-n=\"85\" data-lemma=\"\">DIVI</span>·<span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Traiani\"><span data-text=\"Traiani\" data-n=\"95\" data-lemma=\"\">TRAIANI</span></span>·<span data-text=\"Parthi\n                    ci\" data-n=\"105\" data-lemma=\"\">PARTHI<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>CI</span></span>·<span data-text=\"pronepoti\" data-n=\"115\" data-lemma=\"\">PRONEPOTI</span>·<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"divi Nervae\"><span data-text=\"divi\" data-n=\"125\" data-lemma=\"\">DIVI</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Nervae\"><span data-text=\"Nervae\" data-n=\"130\" data-lemma=\"\">NERVAE</span></span></span><br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span data-text=\"abnepoti\" data-n=\"135\" data-lemma=\"\">ABNEPOTI</span>·<span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Lucio\"><span data-text=\"Lucio\" data-n=\"145\" data-lemma=\"\">L</span></span>·<span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Aurelio\"><span data-text=\"Aurelio\" data-n=\"155\" data-lemma=\"\">AURELIO</span></span>·<br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Vero\"><span data-text=\"Vero\" data-n=\"165\" data-lemma=\"\">[....]</span></span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Augusto\"><span data-text=\"Augusto\" data-n=\"170\" data-lemma=\"\">AUG</span></span></span>·<span data-text=\"pontifici\" data-n=\"180\" data-lemma=\"\">P</span>·<span data-text=\"maximo\" data-n=\"190\" data-lemma=\"\">M</span>·<span data-text=\"tribunicia\" data-n=\"200\" data-lemma=\"\">TRIB</span>·<span data-text=\"potestate\" data-n=\"210\" data-lemma=\"\">POT</span>·<br id=\"al7-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span data-text=\"co\" data-n=\"225\" data-lemma=\"\">CO</span><span data-text=\"nsuli\" data-n=\"230\" data-lemma=\"\">S</span>··II··<span data-text=\"patri\" data-n=\"255\" data-lemma=\"\">P</span>··<span data-text=\"patriae\" data-n=\"270\" data-lemma=\"\">P</span>·<br id=\"al8-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">8</span><span data-text=\"colonia\" data-n=\"280\" data-lemma=\"\">[....</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Augusta\"><span data-text=\"Augusta\" data-n=\"285\" data-lemma=\"\">.]UG</span></span>·<span data-text=\"Tyndaritanorum\" data-n=\"295\" data-lemma=\"\">TYNDAR<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">I͡T</span></span><span data-text=\"decreto\" data-n=\"300\" data-lemma=\"\">D</span>·<span data-text=\"decurionum\" data-n=\"310\" data-lemma=\"\">D</span><br id=\"al9-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">9</span><span data-text=\"curante\" data-n=\"315\" data-lemma=\"\">[....].TE</span>·<span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Marco\"><span data-text=\"Marco\" data-n=\"325\" data-lemma=\"\">M</span></span>·<span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Vale\n                    rio\"><span data-text=\"Vale\n                    rio\" data-n=\"335\" data-lemma=\"\">VALE<br id=\"al10-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">10</span>[...</span></span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Vitale\"><span data-text=\"Vitale\" data-n=\"340\" data-lemma=\"\">....]LE</span></span>·<span data-text=\"curatore\" data-n=\"350\" data-lemma=\"\">CURATORE</span><br id=\"al11-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">11</span>·<span data-text=\"rei\" data-n=\"360\" data-lemma=\"\">R</span>·<span data-text=\"publicae\" data-n=\"370\" data-lemma=\"\">P</span>·</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic000066_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2017-07-21\" src=\"ISic000066_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic000066.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2017-07-21\" src=\"ISic000066-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text of IMusPalermo</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0009-0009-2753-4014\">Alfredo Tosques</a></p>  <p>To Emperor Caesar, son of the deified Antoninus, grandson of the deified Hadrian, great-grandson of the deified Trajan Parthicus, great-great-grandson of the deified Nerva, Lucius Aurelius Verus Augustus, Pontifex Maximus, holder of tribunician power, consul for the second time, father of the fatherland, the Colonia Augusta of the Tyndaritani, by decree of the decurions, under the supervision of Marcus Valerius Vitalis, curator of the public affairs.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>Italian translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0009-0009-2753-4014\">Alfredo Tosques</a></p>  <p>All’imperatore Cesare, figlio del divo Antonino, nipote del divo Adriano, pronipote del divo Traiano Partico, trisnipote del divo Nerva, Lucio Aurelio Vero Augusto, pontefice massimo, investito della potestà tribunizia, console per la seconda volta, padre della patria, la Colonia Augusta dei Tindaritani, per decreto dei decurioni, sotto la supervisione di Marco Valerio Vitale, curatore degli affari pubblici.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>This inscription together with a second, <a href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000065\" target=\"_blank\">ISic000065</a>, both erected by Marcus Valerius Vitalis, honours the emperors Lucius Verus and Marcus Aurelius, who shared imperial power from 161 to 169 CE. They also attest to the presence of a curator rei publicae, an imperial official appointed by Rome to oversee local administration. Cities generally enjoyed a high degree of autonomy, and the reasons for this external supervision are unclear, though they may have been linked to financial difficulties.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 2007.0682 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283</a></li><li> Maggiore 1829 292 no.1 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002795\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002795</a>  </li><li> Mommsen 1883 <a href=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/item/buchseite/650805\" target=\"_blank\">7475</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589</a></li><li> Bivona 1970 67 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002142\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002142</a></li><li> Raepsaet-Charlier 1974 127 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001648\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001648</a></li><li> Manganaro 1988 74 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427</a></li><li> Zambito 2007 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001503\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001503</a></li><li> Fasolo 2013 73-74 no.6 fig.36 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002011\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002011</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1-11  65  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
